divs: Sighting DetailsI walked out side of my job and looking up and to the east I noticed what I believe to be a ramjet contrail. As I was looking at the contrail another plane, not a comercial jet, flew very fast above the first trail. I then ran inside and grabbed my cell phone and snapped 3 pictures. I have seen these trails in the sky many times around this area. The pictures were taken about 30 miles south of MacDill AFB in Tampa which seems to be the area the trails come from.
